review.reviewBody: We ordered the Juillet Cakes Mix or Match and loved this option! Great price! Such beautiful cakes!! Delicious!! Highly recommended!!

The cakes look delicious!  But I'm not sure if I received the Earl Grey Cake or not - doesn't look like the picture!  Kudos to the driver for following the instructions and finding my complex without any issues!
I'm not lying the chicken panini is one of the best I've ever eaten
The Blueberry Checker Box Cake was amazing! Haven't tried the Mango Coconut Box Cake yet, but I'm sure it will be just as delicious!
Their cakes always come in the perfect quantities and are super delicious and yummy
